   833→### ky.stop
   834→
   835→A `Symbol` that can be returned by a `beforeRetry` hook to stop the retry. This will also short circuit the remaining `beforeRetry` hooks.
   864→### ky.retry(options?)
   865→
   866→Force a retry from an `afterResponse` hook.
